OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FA Filipino farm worker in Jersey died
OL,8,Fof carbon monoxide poisoning after he
OL,9,F"impulsively" started a fire to keep
OL,10,Fwarm, an inquest has concluded.
OL,12,FGeorge Michael Monte De Ramos
OL,13,FCastrudes, 37, was killed by the blaze
OL,14,Fat his accommodation on Jersey's La
OL,15,FValette Nurseries site in January last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FHe suffered a hypoxic brain injury
OL,19,Fcaused by carbon monoxide poisoning.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FThe inquest heard how Mr Castrudes'
OL,8,Fportacabin was cold on 19 January
OL,9,F2025, and this influenced the farm
OL,10,Fworker's "impulsive" decision to light
OL,11,Fa fire inside his cabin with a
OL,12,Fmakeshift firepit.
OL,14,FThere was no working smoke alarm in
OL,15,Fthe accommodation, which meant there
OL,16,Fwas little chance of rescuing Mr
OL,17,FCastrudes before he was fatally
OL,18,Finjured, the inquest heard.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FThe Coroner ruled Mr Castrudes'
OL,8,Ffinancial circumstances and the
OL,9,Fstandard of his accommodation at La
OL,10,FValette Nurseries in Grouville
OL,11,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,13,FEarlier in the week, the inquest heard
OL,14,Ffrom an Environmental Health Officer
OL,15,Fwho concluded the farm worker was
OL,16,Fliving in a "property unfit for human
OL,17,Fhabitation".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FThe court also heard how Mr Castrudes
OL,8,Fwould sometimes resort to sleeping in
OL,9,Fthe greenhouse because it was warmer
OL,10,Fthan his cabin.
OL,12,FThe farm worker regularly sent a large
OL,13,Fproportion of his wages back to his
OL,14,Ffamily in the Philippines, which
OL,15,Fultimately left him with little to
OL,16,Flive on.
OL,18,FMr Castrudes' sister, Grace, says the
OL,19,Fconclusion of the inquest means the
OL,20,Ffamily can start to come to terms with
OL,21,Fhis death.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "For now, we are
OL,8,Fjust thankful that it is done already
OL,9,Fand we can begin to move on with our
OL,10,Flives."
OL,12,FThe Coroner made recommendations to
OL,13,Fprevent future fatalities,
OL,14,Fparticularly around the use of
OL,15,Fportacabins to house farm workers on
OL,16,Fthe island during the winter months,
OL,17,Fand to ensure they are meeting the
OL,18,Fminimum requirements of the law.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FCurrently, work permits are in the
OL,8,Fhands of the employer once someone
OL,9,Farrives on the island, and Jersey
OL,10,Fpoliticians are hoping to make changes
OL,11,Fto ensure workers have more control
OL,12,Fover the conditions.
OL,14,FMr Castrudes' sister says overseas
OL,15,Fworkers are unlikely to complain about
OL,16,Ftheir conditions, which exacerbates
OL,17,Fthe problem.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FShe adds: "Overseas Filipino workers
OL,8,Fhave a mindset that no matter how hard
OL,9,Fit is, if they can provide for their
OL,10,Ffamilies back home, they will endure
OL,11,Fit and do their best in the role
OL,12,Fthey're employed for.
OL,14,F"We have the right to be protected by
OL,15,Fthe country that you are working for."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Deputy Beatriz Poree told
OL,8,FITV News: "We need to make sure we
OL,9,Fdon't exploit people and care for
OL,10,Ftheir accommodation - the way they are
OL,11,Ftreated in the workplace is the least
OL,12,Fwe can do as an island."
OL,14,FIn a statement, La Vallette Farm says:
OL,15,F"All of the team at La Valette wish to
OL,16,Fexpress their sincere condolences to
OL,17,FGeorge's family and friends.
OL,26,@oD@^rr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,F"As we have heard, George worked a
OL,8,Fnumber of seasons at La Valette and
OL,9,Fwas a valued and well-regarded member
OL,10,Fof the team. He was a pleasure to work
OL,11,Falongside and his loss has been felt
OL,12,Fdeeply by all at La Valette.
OL,14,F"La Valette has welcomed the
OL,15,Fopportunity to assist the Deputy
OL,16,FViscount in understanding how George
OL,17,Fcame by his death and has sought at
OL,18,Fall times to co-operate fully with the
OL,19,FCoronial process in order to establish
OL,20,Fthe relevant facts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,F"It is hoped that these proceedings
OL,8,Fhave provided clarity and answers for
OL,9,Fthose affected by George's loss."
OL,11,FIn a separate statement, Jersey
OL,12,FCustoms and Immigration Service says:
OL,13,F"We wish to express our deepest
OL,14,Fsympathy to the family and friends of
OL,15,FMr Castrudes during this profoundly
OL,16,Fdifficult time. Our thoughts remain
OL,17,Fwith all those affected by his tragic
OL,18,Floss.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772471475
OL,3,CMigrant farm worker died after
OL,4,C'impulsively' lighting fire to stay
OL,5,Cwarm
OL,7,F"We would like to reiterate that if
OL,8,Fany of our migrant community have any
OL,9,Fconcerns in respect of their
OL,10,Fimmigration conditions, then we ask
OL,11,Fthem to come and speak to us directly.
OL,13,F"We investigate all concerns raised
OL,14,Fwith us, to ensure that everyone is
OL,15,Fbeing treated with dignity and
OL,16,Frespect, and that the strict criteria
OL,17,Flaid out in the Work Permit Policy is
OL,18,Fbeing adhered to."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
